1
00:00:37,300 --> 00:00:40,580
=Reincarnated Love=

2
00:00:40,780 --> 00:00:43,700
=Episode 12=

3
00:00:44,670 --> 00:00:45,510
Put me down.

4
00:00:45,510 --> 00:00:46,710
What are you trying to do?

5
00:00:50,390 --> 00:00:51,230
Ruoli,

6
00:00:51,916 --> 00:00:53,200
can you listen to my explanation?

7
00:00:53,200 --> 00:00:54,040
That's enough.

8
00:00:55,670 --> 00:00:56,510
Huo Linchuan,

9
00:00:57,280 --> 00:00:58,240
every time I see you,

10
00:00:58,240 --> 00:01:00,150
I'm reminded
of my parents' tragic deaths.

11
00:01:01,670 --> 00:01:03,430
I only blame myself
for ever trusting you.

12
00:01:04,790 --> 00:01:05,680
That night,

13
00:01:06,516 --> 00:01:07,630
I went to capture the deputy

14
00:01:07,640 --> 00:01:09,282
who falsely accused
my father of treason.

15
00:01:09,840 --> 00:01:11,480
Someone sent a false report

16
00:01:12,043 --> 00:01:14,083
and diverted the guards
I assigned to your parents.

17
00:01:19,120 --> 00:01:20,560
This is that fake report.

18
00:01:24,900 --> 00:01:26,430
(The Duke was framed.)

19
00:01:26,430 --> 00:01:28,060
(Redeploy guards at the Jiang Mansion.)

20
00:01:28,080 --> 00:01:29,780
(Remain silent. Huo Linchuan)

21
00:01:34,870 --> 00:01:35,710
Ruoli,

22
00:01:36,680 --> 00:01:38,150
can you give me another chance?

23
00:01:39,280 --> 00:01:40,280
I promise I'll help you

24
00:01:41,816 --> 00:01:42,856
and find the real culprit.

25
00:01:57,020 --> 00:01:59,100
(Memorial Tablet of Jiang Huai'an)

26
00:02:03,200 --> 00:02:04,480
Huai'an,

27
00:02:04,760 --> 00:02:06,230
all the stewards are here.

28
00:02:07,120 --> 00:02:08,630
Rest easy.

29
00:02:08,630 --> 00:02:11,080
Leave this household to me.

30
00:02:15,660 --> 00:02:17,340
(Jiang Mansion)

31
00:02:21,560 --> 00:02:22,680
Jiang Huaikang,

32
00:02:24,840 --> 00:02:26,240
how imposing of you.

33
00:02:31,080 --> 00:02:31,920
Ruoli,

34
00:02:33,030 --> 00:02:34,680
your father is dead,

35
00:02:35,280 --> 00:02:37,080
but we can't have no patriarch.

36
00:02:38,000 --> 00:02:40,190
So, I've gathered all the stewards

37
00:02:40,750 --> 00:02:41,643
to officially announce

38
00:02:42,240 --> 00:02:43,470
that I'll be

39
00:02:43,470 --> 00:02:45,060
(Jiang Mansion)
the patriarch.

40
00:02:45,590 --> 00:02:47,030
- Very well.
- Good.

41
00:02:47,520 --> 00:02:48,360
How dare you!

42
00:02:52,240 --> 00:02:53,310
With me here,

43
00:02:53,870 --> 00:02:55,840
you'll never be the patriarch
of this family.

44
00:02:56,240 --> 00:02:57,080
This is absurd.

45
00:02:57,680 --> 00:02:58,870
How could a woman

46
00:02:59,156 --> 00:03:00,489
ever hope to manage the household?

47
00:03:00,870 --> 00:03:01,870
Besides,

48
00:03:01,870 --> 00:03:03,470
you're discarded by your husband.

49
00:03:04,960 --> 00:03:06,140
My dear niece,

50
00:03:06,560 --> 00:03:07,710
your father

51
00:03:08,080 --> 00:03:09,030
has stepped down.

52
00:03:10,190 --> 00:03:11,560
You should learn to accept it.

53
00:03:12,120 --> 00:03:13,280
Despicable.

54
00:03:14,960 --> 00:03:16,710
Now, you have little support.

55
00:03:17,520 --> 00:03:19,560
Do you still want to challenge me

56
00:03:20,080 --> 00:03:21,870
for the position of patriarch?

57
00:03:25,870 --> 00:03:26,710
Very well.

58
00:03:27,560 --> 00:03:29,910
Since you insist on being the patriarch,

59
00:03:31,360 --> 00:03:33,910
I've prepared a generous gift for you

60
00:03:34,280 --> 00:03:37,120
to help you celebrate.

61
00:03:38,710 --> 00:03:39,550
Very well.

62
00:03:40,360 --> 00:03:42,120
At least you know your place.

63
00:03:48,710 --> 00:03:49,550
What's this?

64
00:03:52,660 --> 00:03:55,380
(Ledger)

65
00:03:57,430 --> 00:03:58,310
What is this?

66
00:03:59,150 --> 00:04:01,800
It's every account
after Father fell ill.

67
00:04:06,030 --> 00:04:06,870
On these pages,

68
00:04:07,360 --> 00:04:10,000
every sum you failed
to account for is recorded.

69
00:04:11,400 --> 00:04:12,400
Take a good look.

70
00:04:13,520 --> 00:04:14,800
How dare you investigate me!

71
00:04:16,310 --> 00:04:17,263
How dare you slander me!

72
00:04:18,070 --> 00:04:19,160
Uncle, stop playing dumb.

73
00:04:20,360 --> 00:04:22,420
Out of care for you,

74
00:04:22,830 --> 00:04:24,480
I sorted the accounts ahead of time.

75
00:04:26,070 --> 00:04:26,910
Uncle,

76
00:04:27,390 --> 00:04:28,360
do you still dare

77
00:04:29,070 --> 00:04:30,310
to be the patriarch now?

78
00:04:30,680 --> 00:04:31,520
You...

79
00:04:33,950 --> 00:04:34,790
Uncles,

80
00:04:35,680 --> 00:04:37,560
will you let such a man lead the family?

81
00:04:39,390 --> 00:04:40,230
Ridiculous.

82
00:04:40,720 --> 00:04:42,220
Jiang Huaikang is despicable.

83
00:04:42,231 --> 00:04:43,386
Unworthy to be the patriarch.

84
00:04:43,680 --> 00:04:45,310
- Exactly.
- Remove him.

85
00:04:45,600 --> 00:04:46,580
Remove him.

86
00:04:46,680 --> 00:04:47,750
He must be removed.

87
00:04:47,830 --> 00:04:48,720
He must be removed.

88
00:04:48,800 --> 00:04:50,540
- Remove him.
- Remove him.

89
00:04:50,630 --> 00:04:53,800
- Remove him now.
- Remove him.

90
00:04:54,750 --> 00:04:56,630
- Remove him.
- Remove him.

91
00:05:06,040 --> 00:05:07,310
Jiang Ruoli,

92
00:05:08,430 --> 00:05:10,310
since you are so dutiful,

93
00:05:11,480 --> 00:05:12,510
I'll send you

94
00:05:12,950 --> 00:05:15,750
to be with your parents today.

95
00:05:17,900 --> 00:05:21,220
(Jiang Mansion)

96
00:05:52,430 --> 00:05:53,270
Jiang Huaikang.

97
00:05:53,560 --> 00:05:55,070
My dear niece,

98
00:05:55,680 --> 00:05:57,160
we're out here in the wilds.

99
00:05:57,360 --> 00:06:00,040
Does this scenery please you?

100
00:06:01,310 --> 00:06:02,510
What are you planning to do?

101
00:06:04,480 --> 00:06:07,070
I chose this to be your resting place.

102
00:06:07,070 --> 00:06:08,160
You can say

103
00:06:08,160 --> 00:06:10,230
I've done all I could.

104
00:06:13,270 --> 00:06:14,110
No need to rush.

105
00:06:14,830 --> 00:06:17,600
I'll help you fulfill your piety soon.

106
00:06:17,600 --> 00:06:19,510
You'll join

107
00:06:19,950 --> 00:06:20,870
your ill-fated parents

108
00:06:21,040 --> 00:06:23,070
and

109
00:06:23,680 --> 00:06:25,270
your loyal maid.

110
00:06:27,750 --> 00:06:28,750
It really was you.

111
00:07:29,120 --> 00:07:30,120
Are you alright?

112
00:07:36,950 --> 00:07:37,790
Jiang Huaikang,

113
00:07:39,070 --> 00:07:40,430
you drove Ruyan to her death

114
00:07:40,830 --> 00:07:41,920
and killed my father.

115
00:07:42,360 --> 00:07:43,390
Each one is

116
00:07:43,920 --> 00:07:45,390
a blood-stained score to settle.

117
00:07:46,950 --> 00:07:49,720
You brought this upon yourself.

118
00:07:49,950 --> 00:07:50,790
Wicked woman!

119
00:07:54,430 --> 00:07:56,070
If you hadn't forced me step by step,

120
00:07:57,070 --> 00:07:58,680
I wouldn't have ended up like this.

121
00:08:00,510 --> 00:08:01,600
Take them back in custody.

122
00:08:02,870 --> 00:08:04,950
Jiang Ruoli, Huo Linchuan,

123
00:08:05,430 --> 00:08:07,120
even as a spirit, I won't let you go.

124
00:08:09,240 --> 00:08:10,080
Take them away.

125
00:08:33,030 --> 00:08:34,000
Why are you here?

126
00:08:35,550 --> 00:08:36,510
Something's wrong.

127
00:08:37,120 --> 00:08:39,600
I've been protecting you out of concern.

128
00:08:43,750 --> 00:08:45,080
I was wrong to blame you.

129
00:08:47,870 --> 00:08:48,910
Let's go home,

130
00:08:49,600 --> 00:08:50,550
dear.

131
00:09:13,960 --> 00:09:17,120
I refuse to wait here and do nothing.

132
00:09:27,030 --> 00:09:28,150
It's really you, milord.

133
00:09:28,440 --> 00:09:29,600
I knew

134
00:09:29,600 --> 00:09:30,960
you'd come to rescue me.

135
00:09:30,960 --> 00:09:32,360
You always have a plan.

136
00:09:33,120 --> 00:09:34,510
I warned you long ago.

137
00:09:34,510 --> 00:09:35,670
Target anyone you wish,

138
00:09:35,670 --> 00:09:37,320
but never Jiang Ruoli.

139
00:09:38,150 --> 00:09:39,120
Come on.

140
00:09:39,120 --> 00:09:40,320
She's just a discarded wife.

141
00:09:40,320 --> 00:09:41,550
What use could she be to you?

142
00:09:56,910 --> 00:09:57,870
So, it was you.

143
00:09:59,510 --> 00:10:00,510
No, milord.

144
00:10:01,240 --> 00:10:02,630
No, milord.

145
00:10:02,750 --> 00:10:03,590
Milord.

146
00:10:10,510 --> 00:10:11,840
Lu Huaijin,

147
00:10:12,600 --> 00:10:14,360
you little brat.

148
00:11:26,240 --> 00:11:27,760
♪The dream shattered♪

149
00:11:28,120 --> 00:11:29,800
♪Like illusion, yet true♪

150
00:11:29,800 --> 00:11:31,440
♪Like a restless soul♪

151
00:11:32,320 --> 00:11:33,880
♪How vague♪

152
00:11:34,280 --> 00:11:35,800
♪Rain and blood, drifting wild♪

153
00:11:35,800 --> 00:11:38,040
♪A blade of frost in dreams♪

154
00:11:38,840 --> 00:11:41,440
♪Love and hate entwined♪

155
00:11:41,920 --> 00:11:44,760
♪Rise and fall, yet never fade♪

156
00:11:45,400 --> 00:11:50,160
♪How can I turn the tides
of this fleeting life♪

157
00:11:50,760 --> 00:11:52,280
♪When fate falls apart♪

158
00:11:52,680 --> 00:11:56,240
♪Memories return,
carving tears upon my face♪

159
00:11:56,960 --> 00:11:58,520
♪Yet I can't hold on♪

160
00:11:58,920 --> 00:12:02,640
♪Only warmth remains
where longing once burned♪

161
00:12:03,360 --> 00:12:06,200
♪Life after life♪

162
00:12:06,680 --> 00:12:09,360
♪Fated to meet, but never meant to be♪

163
00:12:10,000 --> 00:12:14,080
♪Still, I refuse to bow or yield♪

164
00:12:14,160 --> 00:12:17,200
♪In this life, love becomes my blade♪

165
00:12:17,360 --> 00:12:18,760
♪To break free from reincarnation♪

166
00:12:18,760 --> 00:12:21,880
♪All past affairs tangled with regret♪

167
00:12:21,960 --> 00:12:23,400
♪Now shatter apart♪

168
00:12:23,520 --> 00:12:27,280
♪By fate and karmic ties confined♪

169
00:12:28,000 --> 00:12:30,800
♪Is this fate or calamity♪

170
00:12:31,080 --> 00:12:33,920
♪Is it life, death, or parting pain♪

171
00:12:34,240 --> 00:12:38,640
♪I ask only for a moment of peace,
as devout as my heart♪

172
00:12:38,880 --> 00:12:41,800
♪In the next life, grant me one kiss♪

173
00:12:41,920 --> 00:12:46,360
♪To kiss the snow upon the brows,
and the depths of your gaze♪

174
00:12:46,560 --> 00:12:52,280
♪For once we kissed,
destiny bound us to never part♪

175
00:12:52,720 --> 00:12:55,440
♪This fleeting life feels but a dream♪

176
00:12:55,680 --> 00:12:58,400
♪Sober or indulge♪

177
00:12:58,840 --> 00:13:04,840
♪I only wish to be with you,
with all my heart♪
